BSCH-HGP Assigment 1 todo list

[] Allow the user to select a specific stock (e.g., Amazon, Tesla, Microsoft, etc.). 
[] Allow the user to input the quantity of the stock purchased. 
[] Allow the user to select the purchase date. 
[] Display the total cost of the purchase. 
[] Allow the user to select the sell date. 
[] Display the total value at the time of sale. 
[] Display the profit or loss. 
[] Optional: Allow selection of multiple stocks for comparison. 
[] Optional: Display additional information (if you choose to add this feature.). 
[] Design file (explain design choice like color, position and all.).
[] Optional: personal space with last trade, gain or loss, last transaction/calculus
[] Optional: see all your placement.